WEBVTT

00:07.760 --> 00:09.479
<i>I need you to go through this</i>

00:09.480 --> 00:11.278
and get me anything
I can use against Tammany.

00:11.280 --> 00:12.714
You are gonna
take on Donovan.

00:12.720 --> 00:13.790
I already did.

00:13.800 --> 00:14.916
Mister Eustace.

00:14.920 --> 00:17.879
I want Corcoran
brought to me, alive.

00:21.120 --> 00:22.873
You wanna live?

00:22.880 --> 00:24.872
- Tell me who sent you.
- Eustace.

00:26.040 --> 00:28.157
You said...

00:28.160 --> 00:30.800
I lied.

00:33.400 --> 00:36.359
The killing can end
or it can continue with you.

00:36.360 --> 00:38.431
Well, you've made
quite a mess, Detective.

00:38.440 --> 00:41.433
Here's to the new
King of Five Points!

00:44.120 --> 00:45.793
<i>Doctor Freeman.</i>

00:45.800 --> 00:47.075
What's wrong?

00:47.080 --> 00:49.390
The president has been assas--

00:50.960 --> 00:52.917
The president
has been assassinated.

00:54.000 --> 01:00.074
